WEBVTT

00:10:59.958 --> 00:11:02.375
and trying to see
a birthday candle behind it.

00:11:03.750 --> 00:11:05.934
Alright, I want to be clear

00:11:05.958 --> 00:11:10.101
that there's nothing inherently wrong
with any of this modern technology.

00:11:10.125 --> 00:11:13.393
With cell phones
or satellites or car radar.

00:11:13.417 --> 00:11:15.601
I'm not sure about kitchen appliances.

00:11:15.625 --> 00:11:16.976
(Laughter)

00:11:17.000 --> 00:11:18.268
I haven't broken down

00:11:18.292 --> 00:11:20.934
and gotten an oven
that talks to my cell phone yet.

00:11:20.958 --> 00:11:23.708
And I use lights at night
like everybody else.

00:11:25.583 --> 00:11:27.309
But here's the thing.

00:11:27.333 --> 00:11:29.309
Some problems in the world,

00:11:29.333 --> 00:11:31.976
like we've heard about today
and you'll hear more about,